               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18360815-name-146" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18360815-name-146" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360815-name-146" type="surname" value="COX"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360815-name-146" type="given" value="THOMAS GEORGE"></interp>THOMAS GEORGE COX</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a boot and shoe maker, and live in Old Brentford. I knew the prisoner when we were boys together, but had not seen him for about fourteen years, till last January—I saw him on Thurs<lb></lb>day, the 21st of July—he came to my house on Wednesday, and said till Friday morning—I then missed the silver spoon.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
