                        <interp inst="t18360815-name-147" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD STOW</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Grant, a pawnbroker in London-wall. I produce a spoon which was pawned by the prisoner for 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. on the 22nd of July, in the name of John Harris, for Margaret Harris.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
